vidhāneneti padmāntargatasavyavāmapārśvavartinyor nāḍyor nirnakhamadhyamātarjanyaṅgulidvayena jihvayā vā cālanena etena prajñāyāḥ kṣaraṇaṃ bhavati | tataḥ padmarandhraṃ snigdhaṃ bhavati | tato vajrāgrāṃ taddravena spṛṣṭam atīva paramaṃ sukhaṃ saṃpādayatīti bhāvaḥ | siddhīti mahāsukham | |

<commentary>dhairyeti antarāntarā vajracālanaviśrāmeṇa paramānandasukhaṃ bhāvayed ity arthaḥ ||
</commentary>

tata iti prajñāvacanāvasānāt | |